title: Gabrielle Union is Going to Need More Wine (Part 1!)
description: This week we’re literally just enthralled by the beautiful angel Gabrielle Union. She’s funny, smart, cool, I could gush for hours or you could just listen to the episode.ALERT. Our first ever T-Shirts are being released to the internet Friday at noon, there’s a limited quantity so keep your eyes on the Instagram.
